    "created_at": "2011-06-25T16:36:03Z",
    "updated_at": "2011-06-25T16:36:03Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Pinging @fperez and @bgranger.  This specifically supports `-pylab` _only_.  Flags still require `--` prefix.  An alternative would be to accept single-`-` prefix for all flags.  This would be more natural for flags like `ipython -i` for force-interactive.  Leaving it as-is gives us a place to add something new in the future.\n"
  },
